snippet.title: War Trigger Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing the new War Trigger game built completely from the ground up.

Wishlist the game and signup for the Playtest on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2623270/War_Trigger

This footage does not represent the final game. The features and specifications of the alpha version are subject to change without notice.
